Interface ICurrentTeamData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StatisticsFacade

    public interface ICurrentTeamData
    This is an auxiliary interface to declare some methods which may be done on a CurrentTeamData Node

    • Method Detail

      • setBallPossession

        void setBallPossession(java.lang.String teamname,
                     double ballPossession)
        Set the percentage of possession of the ball by this team. The possession of the other team will automatically be set. The teams must be registered first ( StatisticsFacade.registerTeams(firstTeamname, secondTeamname) ). Otherwise nothing will be published
        Parameters:
        teamname - the name of the team which has this percentage of possession
        ballPossession - the percentage value of possession of the ball by this team (e.g.: 0% equals 0, 49.54% equals 49.54, 100% equals 100)

      • setPassingAccuracy

        void setPassingAccuracy(java.lang.String teamname,
                      double passingAccuracy)
        Set the passing accuracy of this team. The team must be registered first ( StatisticsFacade.registerTeams(firstTeamname, secondTeamname) ). Otherwise nothing will be published
        Parameters:
        teamname - the name of the team which passing accuracy has to be set
        passingAccuracy - the percentage value of the passing accuracy by this team (e.g.: 0% equals 0, 49.54% equals 49.54, 100% equals 100)
